Upstream-Status: Submitted

 include/extern.h | 1 +
 src/configfile.c | 1 +
 src/memory.c     | 3 +++
 src/net.c        | 1 +
 src/shutdown.c   | 3 ++-
 5 files changed, 8 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

